item.title: Clay-mation coming soon
item.description: So i’m making a movie. Yes thats right, i am making a short animated film for a class project with a fellow class mate, that will eventually end up on youtube for every one to enjoy. I don’t want to give too much away, but will say this: it contains stop-motion play dough. Wait and see!
